---
title: Cajun Spiced Orzo Salad with Greek style cheese and courgette
description: This orzo salad is packed with fun and fascinating flavours. Cajun spice coats the chickpeas and courgette, while pickled onion and Greek style cheese add a little piquancy. Orzo and cherry tomatoes are coated in aioli to tie everything together for a salad that doesn't skimp on taste or texture.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R16_W31_IE_IEXCLF0003-5_Main__10high-db710404.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ie/recipecards/card/64dc86a74b03281706cdd36e.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.ie/recipes/cajun-spiced-orzo-salad-64dc86a74b03281706cdd36e
servings: 2
